  <brief_title>Recombinant Human C1 Inhibitor for the Treatment of Acute Attacks in Patients With Hereditary Angioedema</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II Exploratory, Open-label Study of the Safety and Efficacy of Recombinant Human C1 Inhibitor for the Treatment of Acute Attacks in Patients With Hereditary Angioedema</official_title>
  <sponsors>
