  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this single-center study is to explore the efficacy, safety, tolerability and
      pharmacokinetics/pharmacodynamics of recombinant human C1 inhibitor in the treatment of acute
      attacks in patients with hereditary angioedema.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
